         The value of num1 = 8 and the value of num2 = 5.
 g. Write a C11 statement that multiplies the value of num1 by 2, adds the value of num2 to it, and then stores the result in newNum. Then, write a C11 statement that outputs the value of newNum.
 h. Write a C11 statement that updates the value of newNum by adding the value of the named constant SECRET to it. Then, write a C11 state- ment that outputs the value of newNum with an appropriate message.
 i. Write C11 statements that prompt the user to enter a personâ€™s last name and then store the last name into the variable name.
 //variable declaration
